RL for marketplace search results. [Available Options](https://github.com/VSCodium/vscodium/blob/master/docs/index.md#extensions-marketplace). You must restart Windsurf to use the new marketplace after changing this value."},"windsurf.marketplaceGalleryItemURL":{"type":"string","default":"https://marketplace.windsurf.com/vscode/item","scope":"application","markdownDescription":"Changes the base URL on each extension page. [Available Options](https://github.com/VSCodium/vscodium/blob/master/docs/index.md#extensions-marketplace). You must restart Windsurf to use the new marketplace after changing this value."},"windsurf.searchMaxWorkspaceFileCount":{"type":"integer","default":5000,"description":"Windsurf will attempt to compute embeddings for workspaces up to this many files. This file count ignores .gitignore and binary files. Raising this limit from the default value may lead to performance issues. Values 0 or below will be treated as unlimited."},"windsurf.portalUrl":{"type":"string","default":"","scope":"application","markdownDescription":"**For multi-tenant deployments (Secure, EU, FedRAMP)**: Base URL of your Windsurf portal (e.g., `https://your-company.windsurf.com`).","when":"windsurf:isMultiTenantMode"},"windsurf.enableCursorImportCursor":{"type":"boolean","default":false,"description":"Enable the Cursor-import commands in the palette"},"windsurf.useIndexingV2":{"type":"boolean","default":false,"description":"Use indexing v2"},"windsurf.lifeguard.enabled":{"type":"boolean","default":true,"description":"Enable automatic Lifeguard bug checking on commit."},"windsurf.lifeguard.mode":{"type":"string","enum":["fast","smart","agent"],"default":"agent","description":"Analysis mode for Lifeguard bug checking. Fast mode provides quicker results, smart mode provides more thorough analysis, and agent mode uses AI-powered cascade analysis."},"windsurf.lifeguard.triggerOnCommit":{"type":"string","enum":["enabled","disabled"],"description":"Whether to automatically trigger